      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Full length studio portrait of a group of 16 men. Three of them are wearing plain city clothes. One is dressed in a cassock. The other men are wearing military uniforms and carrying swords. They are sitting and standing around a small cloth-covered table on which some books have been placed.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Among the officials in the picture are Major Konstantin Trofimovich Ryabinkin - Chairman of the military school, Colonel Aleksandr Karlovich von Timler, Major Pavel Adamovich von Pleve, Racho Petrov, Petar Tantilov, Stefan Aleksandrov, Nikola Bochev, Vasil Popovich, Dr. Dimitar Mollov.</ab>
